reviewText: Great movie.  I love Jorja Fox, which is why I purchased the movie.  It was nice to see her star in something other than CSI.  It's a good chick flick and recommend this movie to anyone who likes chick flicks.
Jorja Fox is absolutly amazing in this film. Who'd of thunk that she would be even more beautiful pregnant???  There was not a single scene she was in that she wasn't glowing!!!!!
This is a great romantic comedy about 2 ladies who share their passion and love for food,family and friendship. It's a must see!!!
